<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>PiggyTraval在线安装</title>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<link href="main.css" media="all" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div style="font-size: 1.8em;text-align: center;margin-top: 15%">
			<div style="font-size: 2em;color: #1ea73b">安装事项</div>
			<div>仅支持内网，连接“Aladin”WIFI，不要使用4G</div>
			<div>使用iPhone打开网页，点击按钮，选择安装.</div>
			<div>完成后需要做以下事情：</div>
			<div style="color: #e46e49;font-size: 0.7em;">设置->通用->设备管理->ShenZhen 7Road Technology……->信任“ShenZhen 7Road Technology”</div>
			<hr/>
			<div style="color: #ffffff;font-size: 1em;font-style: bold;background-color: #505050">如果点击安装发生错误，请重新打开本页面，并尝试:</div>
			<div style="color: #ffffff;font-size: 1em;font-style: bold;background-color: #505050">点击右上角的“...”. 然后选择使用Safari打开</div>
			<hr/>
			<div style="height: 10px"></div>
			<center>
				<div style="font-size: 3em;width: 80%;height: 120px;">
					<a class="btn btn-primary btn-large f4 btn-block" style="font-size: 24px !important" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=#{root_url}/#{plist_name}"><div style="height:90px; line-height: 90px;">#{button_name}</div></a>
				</div>
			</center>
		</div>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			function getQueryString(name) {
				var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + name + "=([^&]*)(&|$)", "i");
				var r = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);
				if (r != null) return unescape(r[2]); return null;
			}
			var u = navigator.userAgent;
			var isiOS = !!u.match(/\(i[^;]+;( U;)? CPU.+Mac OS X/);
			if(!isiOS)
			{
				alert("此网页仅支持用iPhone打开");
			}
			else
			{
				var isAuto = getQueryString("auto")=="true";
				if (isAuto) {
					var url = "itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=#{root_url}/#{plist_name}";
					window.open(url,"_blank");
				}
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
